c: 2
v: 255
t: "Allah palibe wopembedzedwa wina koma Iye, Wamoyo wamuyaya, Woimira ndi Woteteza chilichonse. Kusinza sikumgwira ngakhale tulo. Zonse za kumwamba ndi za pansi nza Iye. Kodi ndani angathe kuombola kwa Iye popanda chilolezo chake? Akudziwa za patsogolo ndi zomwe zili pambuyo pawo ndipo zolengedwazo sizidziwa chilichonse pa zomwe zili m’kudziwa Kwake kupatula chimene wafuna. Mpando wake wachifumu wakwanira kumwamba ndi pansi ndipo sizimamvuta kuzisunga zimenezo. Ndipo Iye (Yekha) Njemwe ali Wapamwambamwamba, Ngwamkulu kwabasi, (Ngolemekezeka kwambiri)"